.home-page
  .row
    .banner-section
      = image_tag 'Tech_fest_banner.jpg', class: 'img-responsive img-center', alt: 'TechFest Banner'
      .episode-title
        Episode 15 - Current Theme
      .episode-date
        April 21 - 23 2017
  .row
    .col-md-12
      .page-header
        - if @episode
          %h1
            = @episode.name
            %small
              = "#{@episode.start_date.strftime("%A %d %B")} - #{@episode.end_date.strftime("%A %d %B %Y")}"
        -# else
        -#  %div
            = image_tag 'hackweek-label.png', class: 'img-responsive', alt: 'Hack Week'
  .row
    .col-md-12
      %p.lead
        The event that brings together engineers across locations
        to collaborate, innovate and celebrate software. Across teams or individually, but always without limits. Time to expand
        your horizons! And always remember to have fun!!
    .col-md-12
      %p.lead
        What are you going to hack on?
  .row
    .col-md-8.col-md-offset-2
      %p
        .btn-group.btn-group-justified.btn-group-lg
          = link_to new_project_path, class: 'btn btn-lg btn-info' do
            Start
            %span.hidden-xs
              a Project
          = link_to projects_path(@episode), class: 'btn btn-lg btn-success' do
            Join
            %span.hidden-xs
              a Project
  .row
    .col-md-12
      %p.small.pull-right{style: 'margin-top: 20px'}
        New here &amp; no idea what you're supposed to do?
        = link_to 'Learn more...', about_path
